Cell.Data: Get on the radio to supplies. We're almost out of ammo.
라디오로 보급차에 연락하라우. 탄약이 거의 다 떨어졌다우.
Radar jammer's down in sector twelve!
12 구역에 레이다 방해 전파 발신기 고장!
Keep a look out. Intel reports hostiles heading our way.
조심 하라우야. 정보통에 의하면 적들이 이곳으로 온다.
No sir, they never reported in.
Where the hell is that ammo?
We're waiting for supplies from the harbor.
Officer Kim will be here any minute. Get this place cleaned up!
김동지가 좀 있다 여기 올거라우. 청소하라우
Put out that cigarette, soldier. It's a fire hazard.
담배 끄라우 동무! 여긴 화재 위험 구역이야.
Keep your eyes open, I don't want any surprises.
What the hell is wrong with the power round here?
No idea, sir. It's been on and off all day.
모르겠습네다. 오는 하루 종일 들어왔다 나갔다 합네다.
Yes sir, I'll get right on it.
Sergeant, do a stock take on those rations.
중사 동지, 저 급식 재고 정리좀 하라우.
How long will those rations last?
Another day or two. Hopefully we'll be home by then.
하루 아니면 이틀. 그때엔 집에 가길 바래야지.
This island gives me the creeps.
Locals say this place is haunted.
That would explain all the weird things that keep happening..
그럼 그 이상한 일들이 설명이 되는군.
What's so important about that thing in the mountains?
저 산에 있는 게 뭐 그리 중요하디?
No idea. General Kyong says our country's future depends on it.
모르겠어. 경장군에 의하면 우리 조국의 미래가 달려있다나.
This has got to be the weirdest assignment yet.
이거야말로 가장 별난 임무 중 하나야.
Yeah, something's seriously messed up on this island.
맞어, 이 섬이야 말로 정말 맛이갔어.
Sergeant Lee said he saw a ghost earlier.
How long until the next shift?
Another three hours. Try to stay awake.
Never saw that coming. He was one of the best in the academy.
야 그럴줄 몰랐다. 우리 학교에서 최고 였는데.
Man, this place is so beautiful. I could live here.
야, 여기 정말 아름답다. 여기서 살고도 남겠습매.
You idiot. Wonsan is paradise. This is the home of dog-men.
야 등신아. 원산이 낙원이제. 여긴 개들의 소굴이라우.
Do you think there will ever be Korean reunification?
Not until we smash American imperialistic ambitions.
Another patrol's MIA on the other side of the island.
섬 저편에 또 하나의 MIA가 있다우.
There's definitely something strange going on round here.
정말로 여기에 이상한 일들이 벌어지고 있다우.
Guard duty for sixteen hours straight. I could sleep for a week.
Just another four hours, stay alert.
That mountain is really starting to freak me out.
저 산이야 말로 날 소름끼치게 한다우
Must be a volcano or something.
All these tremors are making me nervous.
What the hell did those archaeologists dig up?
I'm getting sick of this crappy food
You think this is bad, you should try my wife's cooking.
이게 맛없다구. 넨 우리 마누라 음식맛을 봐야해.
Die! You son of a bitch!
